<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SUAL THLAHNAK, DAIHNAK LE THAWNNAK CH96</title>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh he lawmh na duh ah cun, A van thlua chuah rel tuah; Amah bia kha
 kan zumh ahcun, Sithatnak kan hmuh lai.

[C1]
   Sualthlahnak, daihnak, thawnnak, A thiannak le hnangamnak cu; Jesuh
   thawngin kei ca an si, Lunglawm in thangthatnak hla kan sa lai.

[V2]
 A velngeihnak le dawtnak ca, Sual phunphun kha a thlah; Daihnak zong
 kha a si ca ah, Sualthlah tikah kan hmuh,

[C2]
   Sualthlahnak, daihnak, thawnnak, A thiannak le hnangamnak cu; Jesuh
   thawngin kei ca an si, Lunglawm in thangthatnak hla kan sa lai.

[V3]
 Midang thlarau forh khawh awkah, A Thiang Thlarau an pek; Bawi Jesuh
 lawng kannih chungah, A zungzal in a um.

[C3]
   Sualthlahnak, daihnak, thawnnak, A thiannak le hnangamnak cu; Jesuh
   thawngin kei ca an si, Lunglawm in thangthatnak hla kan sa lai.

[V4]
 Jesuh thawng in kannih sinah, Pathian nih pek a duh, Ngakchia bantuk
 kan zumh ahcun, Sithatnak kan hmuh lai.

[C4]
   Sualthlahnak, daihnak, thawnnak, A thiannak le hnangamnak cu; Jesuh
   thawngin kei ca an si, Lunglawm in thangthatnak hla kan sa lai.</lyrics>
